      {
        "position": 4,
        "title": "Easy to activate and accurate",
        "text": "This device is very helpful to keep track of our dog. It works well in our area that is wooded too.The app for the phone is easy to follow and use.",
        "rating": 5,
        "date": "December 16, 2024",
